    "rationale": "Despite multiple credibility factor gaps and the absence of structured provenance on two validation results, the overall hemolysis predictions fall below the clinical threshold across all assessed operating points. The assessment team accepted the package with the understanding that the broken provenance on validation results at operating points 1 and 4 represents an unresolved epistemic gap that should be remediated before regulatory submission.",
